Algorithm
1. Start
2. Input the value of n
3. Initialize sum = 0
4. For i = 1 to n:
      a. If i % 2 == 0:
            i. sum = sum + i
5. Output sum
6. End

Pseudocode
START
    INPUT n
    sum ← 0
    FOR i ← 1 TO n DO
        IF i MOD 2 = 0 THEN
            sum ← sum + i
        ENDIF
    ENDFOR
    OUTPUT sum
END
